Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你則將背負著巴迪的記憶斷片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以現在的姿態開始新的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始得了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別一臉沉著地說出這麼令人絕望的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪會死…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就絕望還為時過早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先確認一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說過巴迪失去了平時的冷靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問她也不好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 逃犯中的一員是原伊茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲達…什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲達魯塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自從知道了這點後她就變得奇怪起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你就夢見了白奧林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲達魯塔和白奧林有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是幻覺重現效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(351,364)}flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原生意識陷入了收縮狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(271,364)}original mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和多雷醫生預想的一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們說的我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來希望你能進行一次旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都這時候還開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地是巴迪的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪的意識正在陷入她自身的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能進入她自己斷片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為作為過濾器的她  意識的機能已經停止的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(260,364)}filter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在其中再次體驗她的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明智地做出對應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能阻止混亂蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼做巴迪就能回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少可以阻止人格的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  這是避免進一步精神融合的唯一對策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用調整槽進行精神潛行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(429,364)}mind dive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,組件啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}System idling start{\r}\N系統空載啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我進入巴迪的記憶 會不會造成進一步的混亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在潛行中也會保持你的意識獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滲透液程序已經調整過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意識  包括你之後的體驗都會顯示出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潛行中也可以進行通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一出現危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就會立刻讓你醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你會看到比夢中更加淒慘的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會一直注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬不要慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  白奧林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的早飯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先去洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}切  知道我是馬格羅馬魯還敢撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在巴迪10歲左右的記憶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然感覺像是在做夢  但馬上就會習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  這個人就是白奧林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}距阿克拉巴魯外苑行政區恐怖事件已經快2年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}中心塔內正在為追悼儀式做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}另外  現在還未能掌握首犯克麗絲蒂菈·利比的行蹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點會遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了嗎  你從今天起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為大家介紹新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奧里奧特拉幼年學校歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那入座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後面  米勒的邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始上課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打開課本52頁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於帝國最後一百年間的內亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那滑板算什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別坐這東西  靠自己的腳走怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是野蠻人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會中這麼簡單的招  你真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想說什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人在撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷德被欺負了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野蠻人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一天就這樣  今後可真令人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麥基烏斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身分擔保人是你  我才答應她入學的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你沒那意思  對普通學生來說可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為阿克拉巴魯恐怖事件的追悼儀式等事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在警惕著阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是時期不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但還希望你們加強監督  不要再次出現輕率的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖事件的追悼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到還不是單純的欺負新學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會因為是阿留多人就遭到歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為你讓她去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了  蜥蜴大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了讓這孩子瞭解真正的社會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  現場需要地方是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  今天起會加大難度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  斯凱爾茲奧教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  麥基烏斯警部補  一會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的對手是程度強化後的西昂Ⅱ型10台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小看它們的話  可是會吃苦頭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和平常一樣記錄資料  不許插嘴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也麻煩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,模擬戰  訓練開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是訓練？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  麥基烏斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦警察進修生的實戰訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進修生的訓練？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪她小時候開始就想當聯邦搜查官嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是想當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是註定要當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她是「依古西奧拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「依古西奧拉」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奧拉是從古代技術中誕生阿留多人優性種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們因為被施於調整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有強韌的肉體和超越常人的各種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的能力當然不能浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此從小就在管理之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察或者與軍隊相關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,職業也早已註定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪連自己的未來也不能選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…「依古西奧拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還能撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  是不是太用力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很痛但是感覺很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受斯凱爾茲奧教官的特訓後得好好治療才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奧拉只能過註定的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被製造出來的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪是這樣出生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更新了最短記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成任務的所用時間  10048
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肉體損害  比上回有所下降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天分真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一定要注意不能對一般市民使用這份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會被當成怪物為世間所忌諱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先前在學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管學校！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麥基烏斯被罵兩句就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  吃好東西去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人怎麼能在這裡恬不知恥地走著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這小鬼真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你們先撞我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是個阿留多人  這小鬼還真狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這小鬼也算是阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙也可能是殺人不眨眼的恐怖分子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個阿留多人小鬼怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是依…依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人不應該打小孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對手是怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不想扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你流了好多血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奧拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太明白  不過面對烏魯卡人或卡魯貝蘭托人也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血止住前要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  我叫巴迪  你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人現在就在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道這話該不該說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人的父親原來是伊茲達魯塔成員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並且協助了逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  到我家去吧  就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓白奧林幫你治療
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林  材料放在這裡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在放學的路上？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有上學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？  去上學吧  很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明每天回來都在抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經和克雷德與米勒成為好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然剛開始被欺負過  但現在關係很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又交到一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  那塔魯是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯  來吃可提吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  白奧林做的可提可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好了  等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  慢慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  那塔魯也吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃點哦  那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯的爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  讓我帶你來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭嗎  這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  他們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紙牌遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星惠果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘樂酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸做的小孩玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他就是那塔魯的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我叫巴迪·希馮  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希馮？ 果然是依古西奧拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（希馮：聯邦學術研究行星希馮。巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉的\N真正含義就是「從希馮中誕生的阿留多人」）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日犬子受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  一起吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真晚啊  塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒工作了正好有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這付得起錢的傢伙終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,運河的工程完成後我也該失業了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛的小妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年紀小小技術一流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是她從烏魯卡人手上救了犬子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女該嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從烏魯卡人手中？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  在這裡沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  反正是貧民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過來吧  小美女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢  那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快給小美女帶路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯  男人就應該陪伴著女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算同樣是阿留多人大家也很懼怕依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可不會在意這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想好將來做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在聯邦警察研修所學習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為警察立功的話  市民權也不是夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  你覺得依古西奧拉的力量是為何而存在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…為幫助朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  可是…不可以沉溺於這份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你…必須找到你作為依古西奧拉而存在的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於這個世界上的人必然有其職責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是我  還是你  甚至那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那並不是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是要靠自己找到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未來能夠靠自己的手來開創
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,珍惜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對你說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我還能再來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是那塔魯的小鎮還是塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些醉酒的叔叔們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  隨時歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的記憶…在我的幼年時代旅行的功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於經歷到中心塔恐怖襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡有被成為「狂戰士」的破壞兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被捲進了那場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了救我  白奧林她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林  我到現在也還…
